column5: Is there a public ramp, or public access to Stevens Bay, or are the roads "gated," with access only through the Lodges that maintain their own ramps/docks on the bay? Thanks, JVC

Last I knew there was a public access near Young's Wilderness Camp. I have never used it, but I see cars and trailers parked there. You might check with Young's Camp to get more detailed directions. Here is a link:http://www.youngswildernesscamp.com/gettinghere.htm
